sequenceDiagram
    actor Developer
    participant Shell as npm / shell
    participant Vitest as vitest
    participant Suites as test/*.test.ts
    participant Modules as parser / server / VM / IDE modules
    participant Coverage as @vitest/coverage-v8

    Developer->>Shell: npm test
    Shell->>Vitest: vitest run
    Vitest->>Suites: discover and execute suites
    Suites->>Modules: import and exercise code
    Modules-->>Suites: assertions / side effects
    Suites-->>Vitest: pass/fail results
    Vitest-->>Shell: summary

    Developer->>Shell: npx vitest run --coverage
    Shell->>Vitest: rerun with coverage enabled
    Vitest->>Coverage: instrument execution
    Coverage-->>Developer: text + html/lcov coverage report
